      "content": "it's just that \"taking a break\" doesn't change the reality. the world doesn't change just because i rest. the gap is still there, and the exhaustion just starts right back up the next morning. sometimes i look at the clock and just wish things would finally, permanently stop. like, i just want everything to be quiet. to not have to feel this weight anymore.",
